  {
    "key": "6ea12a2ba5bba0975f5066e10d71c73968f45748d10b2a9c037c764779cb9b78",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_25.png[/img]While marching through the forest, you come across a body swinging from a branch. It appears it has been there long enough for even the flies to have gotten their fill. %randombrother% notes some sharp suede shoes on the corpse's feet.%SPEECH_ON%Looks like a merchant to me, sir.%SPEECH_OFF%You agree and have it cut down. Upon closer inspection, the eyes have been carved out and tattoos drawn across his chest. Given that you find some crowns still on the body, this was likely to be the work of uncivilized wildmen being spooked by an outsider.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_25.png[/img]While marching through the forest, you come across a body swinging from a branch. It appears it has been there long enough for even the flies to have gotten their fill. %randombrother% notes some sharp suede shoes on the corpse's feet.%SPEECH_ON%Looks like a merchant to me, sir.%SPEECH_OFF%You agree and have it cut down. Upon closer inspection, the eyes have been carved out and tattoos drawn across his chest. Given that you find some crowns still on the body, this was likely to be the work of uncivilized wildmen being spooked by an outsider.\""
  }
